import React from 'react';
import {SidebarContainer, Icon, CloseIcon} from './SideBarElements'
import {NavItem, NavLinks} from "../NavBar/NavbarElements";

const SideBar = () => {

    return (
        <SidebarContainer>
            <Icon>
                <CloseIcon/>
            </Icon>
            <SidebarWrapper>
                <SidebarMenu>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/about'}> About</SidebarLinks>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/discover'}> Discover</SidebarLinks>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/services'}> Services</SidebarLinks>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/signIn'}> Sign In</SidebarLinks>
                </SidebarMenu>
            </SidebarWrapper>
        </SidebarContainer>
    )


}

export default SideBar
